aa(lp87
VSo an app that takes a couple of days to write
p88
aVand then spreads virally,
p89
aVthat's sort of a shot across the bow
p90
aVto the institution of government.
p91
aVIt suggests how government could work better \u2014
p92
aVnot more like a private company,
p93
aVas many people think it should.
p94
aVAnd not even like a tech company,
p95
aVbut more like the Internet itself.
p96
aVAnd that means permissionless,
p97
aVit means open, it means generative.
p98
aVAnd that's important.
p99
aVBut what's more important about this app
p100
aVis that it represents how a new generation
p101
aVis tackling the problem of government \u2014
p102
aVnot as the problem of an ossified institution,
p103
aVbut as a problem of collective action.
p104
aVAnd that's great news,
p105
aVbecause, it turns out, we're very good at collective action
p106
aVwith digital technology.
