aa(lp141
VNow I didn't know very much about government when I started this program.
p142
aVAnd like a lot of people,
p143
aVI thought government was basically about getting people elected to office.
p144
aVWell after two years, I've come to the conclusion
p145
aVthat, especially local government,
p146
aVis about opossums.
p147
aa(lp148
VThis is the call center for the services and information line.
p149
aVIt's generally where you will get
p150
aVif you call 311 in your city.
