aVNow we didn't write this app.
p171
aVThis is the work of the very smart people
p172
aVat the Office of New Urban Mechanics in Boston.
p173
aVSo one day \u2014 this is an actual report \u2014 this came in:
p174
aV"Opossum in my trashcan. Can't tell if it's dead.
p175
aVHow do I get this removed?"
p176
aVBut what happens with Citizens Connect is different.
p177
aVSo Scott was speaking person-to-person.
p178
aVBut on Citizens Connect everything is public,
p179
aVso everybody can see this.
p180
aVAnd in this case, a neighbor saw it.
p181
aVAnd the next report we got said,
p182
aV"I walked over to this location,
p183
aVfound the trashcan behind the house.
p184
