aa(lp209
VNow one of the important things we need to think about government
p210
aVis that it's not the same thing as politics.
p211
aVAnd most people get that,
p212
aVbut they think that one is the input to the other.
p213
aVThat our input to the system of government
p214
aVis voting.
p215
aVNow how many times have we elected a political leader \u2014
p216
aVand sometimes we spend a lot of energy
p217
aVgetting a new political leader elected \u2014
p218
aVand then we sit back and we expect government
p219
aVto reflect our values and meet our needs,
p220
aVand then not that much changes?
p221
aVThat's because government is like a vast ocean
p222
aVand politics is the six-inch layer on top.
