aa(lp247
VNow for those of us who've given up on government,
p248
aVit's time that we asked ourselves
p249
aVabout the world that we want to leave for our children.
p250
aVYou have to see the enormous challenges
p251
aVthat they're going to face.
p252
aVDo we really think we're going to get where we need to go
p253
aVwithout fixing the one institution
p254
aVthat can act on behalf of all of us?
p255
aVWe can't do without government,
p256
aVbut we do need it
p257
aVto be more effective.
